<p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>You have initiated a deposit of more than 10 GB of content in the Stanford Digital Repository.</p>

<h2>Step 1</h2>
<p>You will need to use Globus to transfer the files for this deposit to us.  Click the link below to use single sign on to activate your Globus account.
  Next follow the prompts in Globus to download the "Globus Personal Connect" applications.
  Refer to our <%= link_to 'Help page', Settings.globus.help_doc_url %> if you have questions.</p>

<p><%=link_to 'Globus setup', 'https://globus.stanford.edu/accounts/create.html'%></p>

<h2>Step 2</h2>
<p>Once you have activated your Globus account and downloaded the application,
  <%=link_to 'click this link to let us know you have completed your Globus activation.', work_url(@work)%>.
  We will then email you a link to where you can deposit your files through Globus.</p>

<p>If you have any questions, contact the SDR team at: <%= link_to contact_form_url, contact_form_url %></p>

<p>The Stanford Digital Repository Team</p>
